  "judgment": {
    "summary": "The user asks about the safety of consuming grapefruit juice while taking atorvastatin. The assistant correctly identifies the drug-food interaction and explains the physiological mechanism (enzyme inhibition) and the associated risks (muscle damage/rhabdomyolysis) while advising against the practice.",
